org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Dependability.FailurePropagation

Interface FLABehavior

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FLABehaviorImpl

    public interface FLABehavior
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'FLA Behavior'. replace the old FPTC stereotype

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Constraint
    • Base Class
    • Fptc
    • Base Instance Specification
    • Base Property
    • Base Connector
    See Also:
    FailurePropagationPackage.getFLABehavior()
